{"tid":408761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「十二個鐘內你將會死，除非係你認為最好既朋友黎救你」","createTime":"2017-09-21T13:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T15:53:27.000Z","uid":62064,"like":22,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6672cce170f0a9a1bba6a3001090e7dd2c09f8b0","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"假切依個message經由任何方法通知你所有認識既人，你又幾有信心你可以生存落去？<br />\n <br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心入面最好既朋友一定會救我<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人會黎救我"},{"pid":"0511852557ac1142f858f1f341c43ba665c78631","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假切依個message經由任何方法通知你所有認識既人，你又幾有信心你可以生存落去？<br />\n <br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心入面最好既朋友一定會救我<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人會黎救我</blockquote><br />\n當你從某人收到依何message,你敢唔敢話自己就係個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a06874de6a2deee3c00f3fc105368f07fb7c7c","tid":408761,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88145e431fbc8db807ec19072d279dfac0c8e312","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以叫佢地唔好救</blockquote><br />\n我覺得要加多條 錯既人你立即死 或者死之前你終於知道邊個視你為朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba6258a3c1392a3178ff50938c89d484a59e54e","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"無永遠既朋友，你將可以孤身一人立係不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59bfdcacd531acf983cd7b65bcf443404c78c6d","tid":408761,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"唔知買唔買到機票, 買到都唔知趕唔趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae43d226235d3e37f0d4274f1786634a2acdad6","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知買唔買到機票, 買到都唔知趕唔趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咁既比夠十日又點話 救唔救到自己心裡有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d188178d0fe3fe0d3452fe2803dca5106788c22","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"曾經有人同我講 唔好咁執著人地對你既睇法啊<br />\n<br />\n不如話 唔好咁重視友誼 咁樣仲會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768496af0a8239d68d0b5292ca1a2682e01e1d93","tid":408761,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"最好嘅朋友係男朋友就唔會死<br />\n唔係佢就死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘條屍發臭埋人地先見到個msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5837e6dcbefefede6442afa5c7e11100dbdf10c","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好嘅朋友係男朋友就唔會死<br />\n唔係佢就死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分鐘條屍發臭埋人地先見到個msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男女朋友未必一世 但如果係最好朋友...誰人知曉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bb06d984e412d3c0a8b2140467957820a9ff9e","tid":408761,"uid":62064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"12:24 到底做個三分之一既生活係幾幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後有一日發現 有朋友因為你無